<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、钢琴独奏《悲怆》第一乐章                                                                    贝多芬曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">演奏：全艳</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、女声独唱《曙色》                                                                       晓光词  徐沛东曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">    《千古绝唱》                                                                                   魏冠名词  王超曲</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">    《一杯美酒》                                                                   维吾尔族民歌  艾克拜尔词</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">演唱：王雅倩</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
